Title: Petite Mixed Bouquet - Grower's Choice
Description: A colorful mix of available flowers, filler and greenery - ready for your small vase. Approximately 15 stems, 6-10” tall.

Title: Mixed Bouquet - Grower's Choice
Description: A colorful mix of available flowers, filler and greenery - ready for your standard vase (like a 32 oz mason jar). Approximately 25 stems, 8-18” tall.

Title: Limited-Edition 2020 OBFF Ornament
Description:
To commemorate our inaguaral flower farming year! A great gift on its own, or pair with our Gift Cards to provide something fun to look forward to in 2021!

* 2.5” clear glass ornament with dried 2020 blooms from the farm.

Title: DELUXE - Floral Club Subscription
Description:
The Deluxe bouquets will be a fun mix of 35-40 stems of available flowers, filler and foliage.

Options include:
Wrapped Bundle (in craft paper) $45 or
Arranged Bouquet (in a vase) $60

Weekly:
W1: Early Season (9 wks) - Jun 14-Aug 9
W2: Mid Season (9 wks) - Aug 16-Oct 11
W3: Full Season (18 wks) - Jun 14-Oct 11
* W3 Full season is discounted 10%

Bi-Weekly:
B1: Full Season (8 wks) - Jun 21-Sep 20

Monthly:
M1: Full Season (4 wks) - Starting Jun 28

Title: CLASSIC - Floral Club Subscription
Description:
The Classic bouquets will be a fun mix of 20-25 stems of available flowers, filler and foliage.

Options include:
Wrapped Bundle (in craft paper) $25 or
Arranged Bouquet (in a vase) $35

Weekly:
Early Season (9 wks) - Jun 14-Aug 9
Mid Season (9 wks) - Aug 16-Oct 11
Full Season (18 wks) - Jun 14-Oct 11
* Full season is discounted 10%

Bi-Weekly: Every 2 weeks
Full Season (8 wks) - Starting Jun 21

Monthly:
Full Season (4 wks) - Starting Jun 28

Title: Brides + Blooms
Description: Exclusve event for Ohio Barn bridal alumni and brides-to-be to mingle, take a farm tour and make a petite bouquet! Includes light refreshments. Limit 10 per workshop. Sign up for your date here.

Title: Farm Tour + Petite Bouquet (1 hour)
Description: Schedule a one hour visit to the farm to see it in person and take home a petite bouquet from our inventory! Bring your friends!

Title: Farm Tour + Petite Bouquet Making (2 hours)
Description: Schedule a two hour visit to the farm to see it in person and learn floral arranging basics and create a petite bouquet to take home! Bring your friends!
